text: @UPSHelp I received an email regarding “an important delivery from UPS Customer Service” with a link to download attachments. It seems legit since it’s from packageinfo@ups.com. Is it safe to open the attachments?

@MizzouJB I can see how you would be concerned. Are you expecting a package? If you are enrolled in My Choice it could be an update for a package from that. You can also log in to your My Choice and check your calendar for packages coming to you. ^TV
